---
import BGHome1 from "./BGHome1.astro";
import BGHome2 from "./BGHome2.astro";
---

<section class="relative">
    <div
        class="bg-home-1 hidden xl:block absolute top-0 left-0 max-w-[12.5rem]"
        aria-hidden="true"
    >
        <BGHome1 />
    </div>

    <div
        class="max-w-lg-container mx-auto box-content px-6 md:px-10 text-center xl:text-start flex flex-col xl:flex-row gap-[1.125rem] md:gap-6"
    >
        <h1
            class="font-bold text-10 md:text-16 lg:text-25 leading-none max-w-[10ch] xl:max-w-none mx-auto xl:mx-0 xl:basis-1/2"
        >
            Find the best <span class="text-red-coral">talent</span>
        </h1>
        <p
            class="text-15p lg:text-18p font-semibold leading-28/15 lg:leading-28/18 max-w-[52ch] xl:max-w-none mx-auto xl:mx-0 xl:basis-2/5 xl:ml-auto"
        >
            Finding the right people and building high performing teams can be
            hard. Most companies aren’t tapping into the abundance of global
            talent. We’re about to change that.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div
        class="max-w-lg-container mx-auto mt-24 md:mt-[9.75rem] xl:mt-[9.375rem]"
        aria-hidden="true"
    >
        <div class="max-w-[22.375rem] mx-auto xl:mr-0 xl:ml-auto">
            <BGHome2 />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style lang="postcss">
    @media screen("xl") {
        p {
            @apply self-stretch flex flex-col justify-between;
        }

        p::before {
            content: "";
            width: 3.125rem;
            height: 0.25rem;

            background-color: theme("colors.blue.rapture");
        }
    }

    .bg-home-1 {
        transform: translateX(min(-50%, calc(-75% + 3vw)));
    }
</style>
